127
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:13,200
What's in the past is not

128
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:15,560
worth mentioning.

129
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:19,280
It's just at the last moment,

130
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:23,000
