about killing the emperor.

131
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:27,080
Because Tingyu cracked the case in time.

132
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:29,360
And I realized that

133
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,520
the people of Beichao

134
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:33,400
