135
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:35,520
Shanghua.

136
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:39,320
I want to do what I can to help.

137
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:43,840
No matter what happens,

138
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:44,960
Qijin,

139
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,480
